OL,4,CThe wisdom of Buddha in lockdown
OL,5, The leader of Tibetan Buddhism sees
OL,6, reasons for optimism even in the midst
OL,7, of the coronavirus pandemic. People are
OL,8, helping one another, he tells the BBC's
OL,9, Justin Rowlatt, and if seven billion
OL,10, people on Earth develop "a sense of
OL,11, oneness" they may yet unite to solve
OL,12, the problem of climate change.
OL,14,FThe first time I met the Dalai Lama he
OL,15,Ftweaked my cheek.
OL,17,FIt is pretty unusual to have your cheek
OL,18,Ftweaked by anyone, let alone by a man
OL,19,Fregarded as a living god by many of his
OL,20,Ffollowers.  
